OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776265867
OL,3,C'This story has never been told': the
OL,4,CBible that saved a WW1 soldier from
OL,5,Cbullet
OL,7,FA Bible which is thought to have saved
OL,8,Fthe life of a soldier during the First
OL,9,FWorld War is set to be exhibited at
OL,10,Fthe Dunscore Heritage Centre.
OL,12,FDuncan MacFarlane was serving in the
OL,13,FGordon Highlanders when he was struck
OL,14,Fby multiple bullets.
OL,16,FRecords show he was badly injured, but
OL,17,Fthe bullet which could have killed him
OL,18,Fstruck the Bible he had in his breast
OL,19,Fpocket.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
