PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776265867
OL,3,C'This story has never been told': the
OL,4,CBible that saved a WW1 soldier from
OL,5,Cbullet
OL,7,FIt is thought that the Bible saved
OL,8,FMacFarlane's life.
OL,10,FHis granddaughter, Jo Abbot, now owns
OL,11,Fthe Bible along with other items
OL,12,Fbelonging to her grandfather.
OL,14,FMs Abbot said: "There is his service
OL,15,FBible, held in his uniform chest
OL,16,Fpocket, with a bullet hole in the
OL,17,Fspine. This saved his life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776265867
OL,3,C'This story has never been told': the
OL,4,CBible that saved a WW1 soldier from
OL,5,Cbullet
OL,7,F"He was missing in action for around
OL,8,Fsix months and suffered many other
OL,9,Fwounds. I've seen the missing in
OL,10,Faction telegram but, over the years,
OL,11,Fit disappeared.
OL,13,F"He suffered severe strokes aged fifty
OL,14,Fand that's all I remember of him ` a
OL,15,Ftall, cadaverous man with a useless
OL,16,Fleft arm and side who managed to
OL,17,Fshauchle from his chair to the
OL,18,Fbathroom.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776265867
OL,3,C'This story has never been told': the
OL,4,CBible that saved a WW1 soldier from
OL,5,Cbullet
OL,7,F"He had the most horrific dreams,
OL,8,Fscreaming and shouting and crying.
OL,9,FIt's only as an adult that I was able
OL,10,Fto appreciate what they were about."
OL,12,FAlongside the Bible, MacFarlane's "dog
OL,13,Ftag", medals, and other personal
OL,14,Feffects will go on display.
OL,16,FThese will be unveiled on Sunday April
OL,17,F19 in a small ceremony, with a piper
OL,18,Fand representatives of Gordon
OL,19,FHighlanders Glasgow and Edinburgh
OL,20,FAssociations in attendance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776265867
OL,3,C'This story has never been told': the
OL,4,CBible that saved a WW1 soldier from
OL,5,Cbullet
OL,7,FOnce the items have been displayed at
OL,8,Fthe Heritage Centre for a season, they
OL,9,Fwill move to the Gordon Highlanders
OL,10,FMuseum in Aberdeen.
OL,12,FMs Abbot said: "He was an ordinary man
OL,13,F- a postman - and my grandparents lost
OL,14,Ftwo infant boys, one at six months to
OL,15,Fpolio and another at eighteen months
OL,16,Fto diphtheria.
OL,18,F"This story has never been told and my
OL,19,Ffamily feel it's time it should be. He
OL,20,Fwas my grampa. Seventy two when he
OL,21,Fdied and I was twelve and I loved him."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
